text: Fernand Versini (12 January 1887 - 31 July 1939) was a French field hockey player. He competed in the men's tournament at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:1939 deaths Category:French male field hockey players Category:Olympic field hockey players of France Category:Field hockey players at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:People from Corse-du-Sud Category:Sportspeople from Corsica
